                <h1>Is Google Photos Backup Automatic?</h1>
                <p>Yes, Google Photos offers background backup functionality. When enabled, it automatically uploads your photos and videos to the cloud while you're using your device or even when it's idle. This feature ensures your memories are safely stored without needing to manually initiate the backup. Just ensure you have a stable internet connection for smooth uploads.</p>
